    <item>
      <title>法国总统勒庞在周一截止日期前提高预算要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/france-s-le-pen-boosts-budget-demands-ahead-of-monday-deadline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[极右翼领导人玛丽娜·勒庞在法国分裂的议会中拥有巨大的影响力，她要求总理米歇尔·巴尼耶在周一之前同意她的预算要求，之后再决定是否推翻政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/france-s-le-pen-boosts-budget-demands-ahead-of-monday-deadline</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 07:53:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普时代寻求稳定的投资者选择南非</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/why-south-africa-could-lead-emerging-markets-under-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[长期以来，南非一直被冠以动荡和高风险的新兴市场的称号，但现在，在唐纳德·特朗普担任美国总统的背景下，南非正成为投资者的最爱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/why-south-africa-could-lead-emerging-markets-under-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 07:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟谈判受阻 格鲁吉亚抗议者与警方发生冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/georgian-protesters-clash-with-police-after-eu-talks-were-frozen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格鲁吉亚执政党宣布推迟与欧盟就该国加入欧盟的潜在可能性进行谈判后，抗议者在格鲁吉亚首都与警方发生冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/georgian-protesters-clash-with-police-after-eu-talks-were-frozen</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 07:05:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>约翰内斯堡考虑因供水不足而实施更严格的限水措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/johannesburg-weighs-tighter-water-restrictions-as-supply-falters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了维护老化的基础设施并应对日益增长的需求，南非商业之都正在考虑加强用水限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/johannesburg-weighs-tighter-water-restrictions-as-supply-falters</guid>
