    <item>
      <title>奥尔班任命忠诚的财务主管执掌匈牙利央行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/orban-taps-loyal-finance-minister-as-hungary-central-bank-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班提名长期担任财政部长的米哈里·瓦尔加 (Mihaly Varga) 执掌央行，投资者对这一欧洲最紧缩货币政策之一可能产生的影响保持警惕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/orban-taps-loyal-finance-minister-as-hungary-central-bank-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 06:51:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯国防部长赴朝鲜举行军事会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/russia-defense-minister-visits-pyongyang-as-planes-fly-near-south-korea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯国防部长安德烈·别洛乌索夫周五与朝鲜国防部长进行了通话，这引发了人们对平壤和莫斯科之间深化军事合作的担忧，而俄罗斯战机飞越韩国附近也加剧了紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/russia-defense-minister-visits-pyongyang-as-planes-fly-near-south-korea</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 06:16:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>冰岛大选将迎来绿色能源繁荣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/iceland-election-sets-stage-for-green-energy-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于电力短缺阻碍了北大西洋经济多元化的努力，本周末冰岛举行的大选很可能为其能源产量的提高铺平道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/iceland-election-sets-stage-for-green-energy-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本首相石破茂面临刺激政策的首次重大考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/japan-s-ishiba-faces-first-major-policy-test-with-stimulus-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相石破茂周五在特别议会会议上发表演讲，阐述了他最新的政策愿景，他正在寻求批准 13.9 万亿日元（920 亿美元）的额外预算来资助刺激计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/japan-s-ishiba-faces-first-major-policy-test-with-stimulus-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 01:52:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马科斯在菲律宾与杜特尔特的争执中表现出更友好的语气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/philippines-vp-duterte-won-t-show-up-at-threat-probe-gma-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯 (Ferdinand Marcos Jr.) 希望降低与副总统萨拉·杜特尔特之间的争执，暗示任何弹劾杜特尔特的努力都可能减缓他的改革进程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/philippines-vp-duterte-won-t-show-up-at-threat-probe-gma-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 01:28:22 GMT</pubDate>
